item.description:
@Untrimmed wrote:

[quote=“Elfbow, post:5, topic:436046”]I want the whole place, I need the coordinates for the whole place, please fill it out?

public boolean inFunPk() {
return absX >= HERE && absX <= HERE && absY >= HERE && absY <= HERE;
}

the absx >= will be your southwest y cord absx <= will be your northeast cord absy >= will be you southeast y coord and absy <= will be your northwest y coord

Needed someone to do, because I am having problems[/quote]
All you have to do is go into each corner of the room and get the coordinates. Think of it as a square.
